headline: STLD Issues Q2 Guidance, Expects Higher Steel Operations Earnings
summary: Steel Dynamics projects Q2 EPS of $2.00-$2.04, up from Q1 but down from the prior-year quarter, driven by stronger steel pricing.

headline: Commercial Metals (CMC) Misses Q3 Earnings Estimates
summary: Commercial Metals (CMC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -12.94% and +0.49%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
